Plans after 0.4.0
=================

  New Features:
    [ ] Find, find and replace
          * Regular expressions only?
              - Ignore case
              - Multiline
              - Dot matches newline
          * Target
              - Selection / current project / all open projects
              - Main text, translation text
    [ ] Error correction
    [ ] Capitalization
    [ ] Line reformat
    [ ] Hearing impaired removal


